{{Infobox dungeon |name = Twist Mountain |image = [[File:Twist Mountain.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Twist Mountain. |tokens = 356,500 |location = Unova Route 7 }} '''Twist Mountain''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
